title: Targus Numeric Keypad - Unboxing and Initial thoughts
description:
In this video I am unboxing the Targus Numpad which I intend on using during my Twitch streams!

I know its not the most amazing piece of tech to unbox, but It will definitely become rather useful for myself.

Hope you liked the video and if you did make sure to leave a thumbs up, drop a comment or maybe even subscribe!

Array_J
